{
  "stem": "8784.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we didn't know exactly where to run, because it was-- mass confusion took over.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And no one-- no one was there to tell us where we should go or where we shouldn't go.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But the bombs were flying all around us, so we had to run some place.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We-- we actually, as a family, we began marching towards the city of Krakow, which probably after rethinking, was the wrong place to go, because we should have gone more into the country.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But we went to the city of Krakow hoping to escape the bombs.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But that was not true.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And in a short time after that, maybe two weeks into the war, we had to go back to our home in Borek Falecki and stay there from there on to continue the war.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Life, life became very difficult immediately, two weeks after the war or so.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It became very difficult, because number one, Jewish children were no longer permitted into any public schools.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Food was in extremely short supply, so the family would rely on the children going and standing on line someplace where there-- where there were food-- where there was food available.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We stood on line sometimes throughout the whole night to be able to buy a bread or milk or kerosene.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And mostly the children had to do that, because my father with a beard could not stand in a line together with Poles, because he would be recognized as a Jewish person.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And he would not be welcome in the line.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the children were best equipped to stand in those lines and not being detected as being Jewish.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sometimes we would stand as long as a-- as a-- most of the night on line to be able to buy bread in the morning.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
